app.comment:
Rail Baron Calculator is an app designed to be used as an adjunct to the classic board game rail baron. It replaces the slow and frustrating process of sifting through reference tables to determine destinations and rewards for completing a journey.

Features in v1.0 include:
-Simple touch friendly interface
-Ability to generate next destination
-Displays current trip and home city for 2-6 players
-Displays reward for completing current journey
-Undo and redo buttons in case of accidental clicks

If you find any errors in the program or the data (eg incorrect reward amount for a journey) please let me know. The data entry was long and tedious and I apologise for any mistakes.
